            I = Val(I$)
        Loop Until I >= 1 And I <= 4

        Select Case I

            Case 1:
                Call SwitchBatters

            Case 2:
                Call SwitchPitchers

            Case 3:

                If TS <> 0 Then

                    Cls

                    Open diskPaths$(1) + teamStatFile$ For Output As #1

                    Print #1, targetTeam$
                    Print #1, teamWins
                    Print #1, teamLosses

                    For I = 0 To 22:
                        Print #1, batterNames$(I)
                        Print #1, statB(I)
                    Next I

